signs.value: Allows application to send SMS messages. Malicious applications may cost you money by sending messages without your confirmation.
Allows application to receive and process SMS messages. Malicious applications may monitor your messages or delete them without showing them to you.
Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

Allows the application to call phone numbers without your intervention. Malicious applications may cause unexpected calls on your phone bill. Note that this does not allow the application to call emergency numbers.
Allows application to read SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. Malicious applications may read your confidential messages.
Allows application to write to SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. Malicious applications may delete your messages.
Allows an application to modify the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your contact data.
Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.
Allows an application to write to the SD card.
Allows application to receive and process MMS messages. Malicious applications may monitor your messages or delete them without showing them to you.

permissions.description: Allows application to send SMS messages. Malicious applications may cost you money by sending messages without your confirmation.
permissions.name: android.permission.SEND_SMS

permissions.description: Allows application to receive and process SMS messages. Malicious applications may monitor your messages or delete them without showing them to you.
permissions.name: android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS

permissions.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.
permissions.name: android.permission.READ_CONTACTS

permissions.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.
permissions.name: android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE

permissions.description: Allows the application to control the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can switch networks, turn the phone radio on and off and the like, without ever notifying you.
permissions.name: android.permission.MODIFY_PHONE_STATE

permissions.description: Allows the application to call phone numbers without your intervention. Malicious applications may cause unexpected calls on your phone bill. Note that this does not allow the application to call emergency numbers.
permissions.name: android.permission.CALL_PHONE

permissions.description: Allows application to read SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. Malicious applications may read your confidential messages.
permissions.name: android.permission.READ_SMS

permissions.description: Allows application to write to SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. Malicious applications may delete your messages.
permissions.name: android.permission.WRITE_SMS

permissions.description: Allows an application to modify the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your contact data.
permissions.name: android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS

permissions.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.
permissions.name: android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS

permissions.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.
permissions.name: android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE

permissions.description: Allows application to receive and process MMS messages. Malicious applications may monitor your messages or delete them without showing them to you.
permissions.name: android.permission.RECEIVE_MMS

permissions.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.
permissions.name: android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED
